gov.lbl.glammdb.kegg.kgml
Class KgmlPlusDocument

java.lang.Object
  gov.lbl.glammdb.kegg.kgml.KgmlPlusDocument

public final class KgmlPlusDocument
extends java.lang.Object

KGML+ document handler - extracts svg and reaction network information and stores GLAMM annotated maps in the GLAMM database via the KgmlReactions and KgmlSvg handlers.

Author:
jtbates
